  "text": [
    "The giant world",
    "is no damned genius",
    "with its basket of latitude,",
    "its schedule for wanting",
    "to be touched.",
    "Now, slow asleep",
    "I\u2019m song",
    "to break in on,",
    "a strength less lost",
    "than gone.",
    "I borrow minute, hour,",
    "day, day.",
    "The waves as cruel replacements pass",
    "for crutches."
  ],
  "title": "Almost As If I\u2019ve Been Given an Horizon",
  "year": ""
}